latestIgtvVideos.caption: Okay you guys... go easy on me 🙈🤪 I’m new to this whole video thing, but me and my friends were at the salon playing with my new phone one night and thought we might try it out! If I had known we were going to do this and i’d be in it I wouldn’t have come in with a fresh spray tan and would’ve waved my hair a little more, but whatevs! Serving some serious Oompa Loompa looks lmao. Anyways... I LOVE doing extensions! These came out so beautiful for a beautiful bride to be!! 👰🏽💍💍💍 Hope you guys enjoy the process xoxox Happy almost Thanksgiving 🦃

latestPosts.caption:
New Accounts: Welcome to Salon Xtensions Pro! 🕊️

I’m thrilled to welcome you into our professional network. As your dedicated account lead, I’m here to ensure you have the support, resources, and insider knowledge you need to grow and scale with confidence. 💡

Whether you’re navigating our product lines, waiting on your color ring, or need help matching shades — I’ve got you covered. I personally carry every ring in our range: from machine and hand-tied wefts to mesh closures, men’s and women’s toppers, and beyond.

Need a restock ETA? You’ll get accurate, up-to-date info.

Thinking about launching your own brand? I’ll walk you through our private label program and help you create a seamless, high-impact rollout. 🩵

And because as a stylist myself I understand how full your schedule is — from back-to-back clients, taking care of the kids, color on your hands, eating snacks between double booking, to the inevitable late-night order crunch — we make the process EASIER. 

With a credit card authorization form on file, you can simply text in your orders. No site navigation, no payment entry — just efficient, done-for-you service. Your extensions ordered and shipped straight to your door with one simple text or email! 

At Salon Xtensions, we don’t just supply product, we support professionals. I’m here to help you streamline operations, increase revenue, and serve your clients at the highest level.

Let’s build something powerful — together.

latestPosts.caption:
Did you know you can start your own extension brand with as little as a $5K investment?

✨ Your name, your logo, your vision brought to life. ✨

With me and the team at Salon Xtensions guiding you every step of the way—from branding and product selection to fulfillment and website design—we make it easy and exciting to build something that’s yours.
We’re truly here for it all.
💻📦

As a stylist of almost 10 years with a deep love for the creative side of the industry, I live for helping you curate your products and choose the perfect tool kit with your brand front and center. The tools with your name, I can’t 🥹 I swoon! Lol, I love tools. 

The details matter—and we make them beautiful. 🎨✨

It’s honestly so dreamy. Building a brand feels like investing in your future—and for us beauty school girlies, it’s our version of buying stock.
(And yes, we believe in long-term index funds over here too, but that’s a convo for another day.)
Your brand is your legacy. Your name. Your touch. Your STOCK.
💼

Ready to start building something that’s truly yours? Hit the link in my bio and book your 15 minute discovery call, or DM me “BRAND” to get started! 

Soft life with structure. Let’s dream it up together. 🌷
